{"tid":1427660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[朋友被捕求片！]8月3日晚上黃大仙中心及巴士總站之間的拍攝影片","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T18:56:09.000Z","uid":82649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ddee9af48e76ffef9c6f3719a6a839f48bb5897","tid":1427660,"uid":82649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"代出POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n急急急！<br />\n呼籲如果有人於8月3日晚上23:00-23:15在黃大仙中心及巴士總站之間，花槽附近的拍攝影片或相片，請分享作證供。<br />\n<br />\n青年男子和女朋友在黃大仙中心吃完飯回家途中剛巧遇到騷亂，在花槽間探望究竟之際，突然被防暴警察上前用槍指頭，隨即從後被壓在地上亂打及拘捕二人，及後被落案控告襲警及非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n如有拍攝經過，請好心分享影像或相片作供。<br />\nTelegram（Secret Chat）：needhelp831115<br />\n<br />\n因為好快要提堂，路見不平拔刀相助，好心有好報！<br />\n請廣為傳播<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />萬分感激！"},{"pid":"13197d0766d1df68c30561e1521fabae702ea265","tid":1427660,"uid":82649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:24:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"014ee37ebe2606e2d0e84653031de963fab9ef64","tid":1427660,"uid":181370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1fcd8600bc730a951ec898a22e739dbc4921a425","tid":1427660,"uid":82649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00119bcf9efd6c4e3f662dcf83ee3c72d6103bb","tid":1427660,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"唔係要由控方搜證嗎?"},{"pid":"469001c975696163990db73ea6e04d5fcc40db6e","tid":1427660,"uid":82649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d00119bcf9efd6c4e3f662dcf83ee3c72d6103bb","tid":1427660,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:33:45.000Z","msg":"唔係要由控方搜證嗎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"警權過大 黑警話乜就乜<br />\n有唔少俾人拉咗嘅都係路過或者咁啱喺現場<br />\n都未搞清楚咩事就俾人拉甚至俾人告